<h1>About us</h1>
Founded in 1927 in Bologna, Italy, Furla is one of the major players in the worldwide 
leather goods market, standing for its strictly Made-in-Italy creativity. 
The company is present in 100 countries with more than 450 single-brand shops situated on the most 
prestigious international shopping streets, a distribution network with over a thousand official points 
of sales and important growing channels such as travel retail and e-commerce. Furla presents its new 
engaging vision, essential to each employee to achieve the best results and pursue professional growth.